The Hawks are also functioning at half of their required capacity. Senior police offivials appeared before Parliament's Police Committee to discuss matters around the latest crime statistics, released last week. According to the 2018/19 figures, murder has increased by nearly 700 cases, bringing the total to 21022. Sexual offences have spiked by more than 2000 to 52 420. Zalene Merrington has more... --SABC--